node.text:
Supporting my friend @figandstarbeauty 

You can use code Nala for 25% off your entire order @figandstarbeauty

The founder of Fig & Star is a Los Angeles County animal shelter volunteer and a hairstylist of 25 years.  She saw a need to help save as many animals as possible and, with this, combined her love for hair and passion to save animals to create Fig and Star. Partial proceeds from sales go toward helping animals get into rescues or out of the shelter system. Animals who have been helped by Fig and Star are shown on the highlight section of Fig & Star’s Instagram and donations are shown on the company’s website. Nala came from a Los Angeles County shelter too!
